About Us

About Venice Ranch
If you're interested in a 3rd generation family owned well-maintained, 55 + retirement, lot rental and manufactured housing community, look no more you have found us.
Venice Ranch Mobile Home Estates
is a beautifully manufactured mobile home community for 55+ residents. We are conveniently located near shopping, beaches, boating, fishing, golf courses, theater, library, hospital, and restaurants.
With an ideal location in South Sarasota County, we are just 1/4 of a mile from Venice City limits, 2 1/4 miles east of 41 By-Pass, and 3/4 of a mile west of Jacaranda Blvd. (Exit 193 of I-75). Sarasota-Bradenton International Airport is easily accessible from I-75 at Exit 213. Contact
Venice Ranch Mobile Home Estates
today to schedule a tour!
CALL US

photoswipe markup
Root element of PhotoSwipe. Must have class pswp.
Background of PhotoSwipe. 
         It's a separate element as animating opacity is faster than rgba().
Slides wrapper with overflow:hidden.
Container that holds slides. 
            PhotoSwipe keeps only 3 of them in the DOM to save memory.
            Don't modify these 3 pswp__item elements, data is added later on.
Default (PhotoSwipeUI_Default) interface on top of sliding area. Can be changed.
Controls are self-explanatory. Order can be changed.
Preloader demo http://codepen.io/dimsemenov/pen/yyBWoR
